{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":949,"text":"(Rainforest noises)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":9680,"text":"In the summer of 2011,\nas a tourist,"},{"time":13167,"text":"I visited the rainforests of Borneo\nfor the very first time,"},{"time":17593,"text":"and as you might imagine,"},{"time":19641,"text":"it was the overwhelming sounds\nof the forest that struck me the most."},{"time":24911,"text":"There's this constant cacophony of noise."},{"time":27721,"text":"Some things actually do stick out."},{"time":30136,"text":"For example, this here is a big bird,\na rhinoceros hornbill."},{"time":34562,"text":"This buzzing is a cicada."},{"time":39434,"text":"This is a family of gibbons."},{"time":42047,"text":"It's actually singing to each other\nover a great distance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47341,"text":"The place where this was recorded\nwas in fact a gibbon reserve,"},{"time":50334,"text":"which is why you can hear so many of them,"},{"time":52372,"text":"but in fact the most important noise that \nwas coming out of the forest that time"},{"time":57302,"text":"was one that I didn't notice,"},{"time":58834,"text":"and in fact nobody there\nhad actually noticed it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62373,"text":"So, as I said, this was a gibbon reserve."},{"time":64361,"text":"They spend most of their time\nrehabilitating gibbons,"},{"time":67170,"text":"but they also have\nto spend a lot of their time"},{"time":69731,"text":"protecting their area from illegal logging\nthat takes place on the side."},{"time":73423,"text":"And so if we take the sound of the forest"},{"time":75466,"text":"and we actually turn down the gibbons,\nthe insects, and the rest,"},{"time":79023,"text":"in the background, the entire time,\nin recordings you heard,"},{"time":82689,"text":"was the sound of a chainsaw\nat great distance."},{"time":86403,"text":"They had three full-time guards\nwho were posted around this sanctuary"},{"time":90397,"text":"whose job was in fact\nto guard against illegal logging,"},{"time":94599,"text":"and one day, we went walking,\nagain as tourists, out into the forest,"},{"time":98058,"text":"and within five minutes' walk,"},{"time":100311,"text":"we stumbled upon somebody\nwho was just sawing a tree down,"},{"time":103690,"text":"five minutes' walk, a few hundred meters\nfrom the ranger station."},{"time":106951,"text":"They hadn't been able\nto hear the chainsaws,"},{"time":109009,"text":"because as you heard,\nthe forest is very, very loud."}]},{"cues":[{"time":112826,"text":"It struck me as quite unacceptable\nthat in this modern time,"},{"time":116745,"text":"just a few hundred meters away \nfrom a ranger station in a sanctuary,"},{"time":121217,"text":"that in fact nobody could hear it when\nsomeone who has a chainsaw gets fired up."},{"time":125022,"text":"It sounds impossible,\nbut in fact, it was quite true."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129689,"text":"So how do we stop illegal logging?"},{"time":131523,"text":"It's really tempting, as an engineer,\nalways to come up with a high-tech,"},{"time":134952,"text":"super-crazy high-tech solution,"},{"time":136713,"text":"but in fact, you're in the rainforest."},{"time":138663,"text":"It has to be simple,\nit has to be scalable,"},{"time":141040,"text":"and so what we also noticed\nwhile were there was that"},{"time":144048,"text":"everything we needed was already there."},{"time":146374,"text":"We could build a system\nthat would allow us to stop this"},{"time":149125,"text":"using what's already there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151407,"text":"Who was there? What was \nalready in the forest?"},{"time":153639,"text":"Well, we had people."},{"time":154787,"text":"We had this group there that was \ndedicated, three full-time guards,"},{"time":158072,"text":"that was dedicated to go and stop it,"},{"time":159846,"text":"but they just needed to know\nwhat was happening out in the forest."},{"time":162960,"text":"The real surprise, this is the big one,"},{"time":164853,"text":"was that there was connectivity\nout in the forest."},{"time":167236,"text":"There was cell phone service\nway out in the middle of nowhere."},{"time":170150,"text":"We're talking hundreds of kilometers\nfrom the nearest road,"},{"time":173081,"text":"there's certainly no electricity,\nbut they had very good cell phone service,"},{"time":176653,"text":"these people in the towns\nwere on Facebook all the time,"},{"time":179276,"text":"they're surfing the web on their phones,"},{"time":181226,"text":"and this sort of got me thinking\nthat in fact it would be possible"},{"time":184335,"text":"to use the sounds of the forest,"},{"time":186494,"text":"pick up the sounds \nof chainsaws programmatically,"},{"time":188886,"text":"because people can't hear them,"},{"time":190534,"text":"and send an alert."},{"time":192221,"text":"But you have to have a device\nto go up in the trees."},{"time":194803,"text":"So if we can use some device\nto listen to the sounds of the forest,"},{"time":198454,"text":"connect to the cell phone\nnetwork that's there,"},{"time":200687,"text":"and send an alert to people on the ground,"},{"time":202721,"text":"perhaps we could have a solution\nto this issue for them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206271,"text":"But let's take a moment\nto talk about saving the rainforest,"},{"time":209551,"text":"because it's something that we've\ndefinitely all heard about forever."},{"time":213393,"text":"People in my generation\nhave heard about saving the rainforest"},{"time":216312,"text":"since we were kids,"},{"time":218212,"text":"and it seems that the message\nhas never changed:"},{"time":220460,"text":"We've got to save the rainforest,\nit's super urgent,"},{"time":222982,"text":"this many football fields\nhave been destroyed yesterday."},{"time":225688,"text":"and yet here we are today,\nabout half of the rainforest remains,"},{"time":228992,"text":"and we have potentially more urgent \nproblems like climate change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":233319,"text":"But in fact, this is the little-known fact\nthat I didn't realize at the time:"},{"time":237228,"text":"Deforestation accounts \nfor more greenhouse gas"},{"time":240189,"text":"than all of the world's planes,\ntrains, cars, trucks and ships combined."},{"time":244229,"text":"It's the second highest contributor\nto climate change."},{"time":246945,"text":"Also, according to Interpol,"},{"time":249778,"text":"as much as 90 percent of the logging\nthat takes place in the rainforest"},{"time":253307,"text":"is illegal logging,\nlike the illegal logging that we saw."},{"time":257088,"text":"So if we can help people in the forest\nenforce the rules that are there,"},{"time":261132,"text":"then in fact we could eat heavily\ninto this 17 percent"},{"time":265056,"text":"and potentially have a major impact\nin the short term."},{"time":267667,"text":"It might just be the cheapest,\nfastest way to fight climate change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":272832,"text":"And so here's the system that we imagine."},{"time":274830,"text":"It looks super high tech."},{"time":276024,"text":"The moment a sound of a chainsaw\nis heard in the forest,"},{"time":278657,"text":"the device picks up the sound\nof the chainsaw,"},{"time":280829,"text":"it sends an alert through the standard\nGSM network that's already there"},{"time":284436,"text":"to a ranger in the field"},{"time":286523,"text":"who can in fact show up in real time\nand stop the logging."},{"time":289340,"text":"It's no more about going out\nand finding a tree that's been cut."},{"time":293249,"text":"It's not about seeing \na tree from a satellite"},{"time":295425,"text":"in an area that's been clear cut,"},{"time":297061,"text":"it's about real-time intervention."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299669,"text":"So I said it was the cheapest\nand fastest way to do it,"},{"time":302390,"text":"but in fact, actually, as you saw,\nthey weren't able to do it,"},{"time":305315,"text":"so it may not be so cheap and fast."},{"time":307199,"text":"But if the devices in the trees\nwere actually cell phones,"},{"time":310635,"text":"it could be pretty cheap."},{"time":312191,"text":"Cell phones are thrown away\nby the hundreds of millions every year,"},{"time":316478,"text":"hundreds of millions in the U.S. alone,"},{"time":318599,"text":"not counting the rest of the world,\nwhich of course we should do,"},{"time":321780,"text":"but in fact, cell phones are great."},{"time":324311,"text":"They're full of sensors."},{"time":325644,"text":"They can listen\nto the sounds of the forest."},{"time":327796,"text":"We do have to protect them."},{"time":329178,"text":"We have to put them in this box\nthat you see here,"},{"time":331585,"text":"and we do have to power them."},{"time":333152,"text":"Powering them is one of the greater\nengineering challenges"},{"time":335915,"text":"that we had to deal with,"},{"time":337215,"text":"because powering a cell phone\nunder a tree canopy,"},{"time":339967,"text":"any sort of solar power\nunder a tree canopy,"},{"time":342219,"text":"was an as-yet-unsolved problem,"},{"time":344029,"text":"and that's this unique\nsolar panel design that you see here,"},{"time":346886,"text":"which in fact is built also from recycled\nbyproducts of an industrial process."},{"time":351205,"text":"These are strips that are cut down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353829,"text":"So this is me putting it all together"},{"time":357335,"text":"in my parents' garage, actually."},{"time":359216,"text":"Thanks very much to them\nfor allowing me to do that."},{"time":361793,"text":"As you can see,\nthis is a device up in a tree."},{"time":366149,"text":"What you can see from here, perhaps,\nis that they are pretty well obscured"},{"time":369734,"text":"up in the tree canopy at a distance."},{"time":371536,"text":"That's important, because although\nthey are able to hear chainsaw noises"},{"time":375013,"text":"up to a kilometer in the distance,"},{"time":376783,"text":"allowing them to cover\nabout three square kilometers,"},{"time":379303,"text":"if someone were to take them,\nit would make the area unprotected."}]},{"cues":[{"time":383281,"text":"So does it actually work?"},{"time":386034,"text":"Well, to test it,\nwe took it back to Indonesia,"},{"time":389006,"text":"not the same place, but another place,"},{"time":391119,"text":"to another gibbon reserve"},{"time":392790,"text":"that was threatened daily\nby illegal logging."},{"time":396505,"text":"On the very second day, it picked up\nillegal chainsaw noises."},{"time":400424,"text":"We were able to get a real-time alert."},{"time":402623,"text":"I got an email on my phone."},{"time":403970,"text":"Actually, we had just climbed the tree.\nEveryone had just gotten back down."},{"time":407686,"text":"All these guys are smoking cigarettes,"},{"time":409926,"text":"and then I get an email,\nand they all quiet down,"},{"time":412783,"text":"and in fact you can hear the chainsaw"},{"time":414887,"text":"really, really faint in the background,"},{"time":416816,"text":"but no one had noticed it \nuntil that moment."},{"time":419121,"text":"And so then we took off\nto actually stop these loggers."},{"time":422395,"text":"I was pretty nervous."},{"time":423904,"text":"This is the moment where we've actually\narrived close to where the loggers are."},{"time":428130,"text":"This is the moment where you can see\nwhere I'm actually regretting"},{"time":431244,"text":"perhaps the entire endeavor."},{"time":433245,"text":"I'm not really sure what's on\nthe other side of this hill."},{"time":435988,"text":"That guy's much braver than I am."},{"time":437951,"text":"But he went, so I had to go, walking up,"},{"time":442131,"text":"and in fact, he made it over the hill,"},{"time":444290,"text":"and interrupted the loggers in the act."},{"time":447527,"text":"For them, it was such a surprise --"},{"time":449189,"text":"they had never, ever\nbeen interrupted before --"},{"time":451569,"text":"that it was such an impressive\nevent for them,"},{"time":453734,"text":"that we've heard from our partners\nthey have not been back since."},{"time":456850,"text":"They were, in fact, great guys."},{"time":458342,"text":"They showed us how\nthe entire operation works,"},{"time":460522,"text":"and what they really convinced us\non the spot was that"},{"time":463096,"text":"if you can show up\nin real time and stop people,"},{"time":465341,"text":"it's enough of a deterrent\nthey won't come back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":469529,"text":"So --"},{"time":471085,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":477586,"text":"Word of this spread, possibly\nbecause we told a lot of people,"},{"time":481440,"text":"and in fact, then some really\namazing stuff started to happen."},{"time":484877,"text":"People from around the world\nstarted to send us emails, phone calls."},{"time":488546,"text":"What we saw was that people\nthroughout Asia,"},{"time":490635,"text":"people throughout Africa,\npeople throughout South America,"},{"time":493377,"text":"they told us that they could use it too,"},{"time":495288,"text":"and what's most important,"},{"time":496568,"text":"what we'd found that\nwe thought might be exceptional,"},{"time":499066,"text":"in the forest there was\npretty good cell phone service."},{"time":501648,"text":"That was not exceptional, we were told,"},{"time":503525,"text":"and that particularly is on the periphery\nof the forests that are most under threat."},{"time":507468,"text":"And then something \nreally amazing happened,"},{"time":509768,"text":"which was that people started sending us\ntheir own old cell phones."},{"time":513251,"text":"So in fact what we have now is a system"},{"time":515201,"text":"where we can use people on the ground,\npeople who are already there,"},{"time":518544,"text":"who can both improve\nand use the existing connectivity,"},{"time":521609,"text":"and we're using old cell phones\nthat are being sent to us"},{"time":524286,"text":"by people from around the world"},{"time":525779,"text":"that want their phones to be doing \nsomething else in their afterlife,"},{"time":529072,"text":"so to speak."},{"time":529826,"text":"And if the rest of the device\ncan be completely recycled,"},{"time":532755,"text":"then we believe it's\nan entirely upcycled device."}]},{"cues":[{"time":535471,"text":"So again, this didn't come\nbecause of any sort of high-tech solution."},{"time":539125,"text":"It just came from using\nwhat's already there,"},{"time":541438,"text":"and I'm thoroughly convinced\nthat if it's not phones,"},{"time":544294,"text":"that there's always\ngoing to be enough there"},{"time":546663,"text":"that you can build similar solutions"},{"time":548474,"text":"that can be very effective\nin new contexts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":550540,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":552676,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}